{"tid":786647,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普：通俄門調查應「轉向中國」","createTime":"2018-08-20T05:39:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-20T09:22:42.000Z","uid":62257,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0c0bdb1b440a4e02ec106f90271c785fb447096d","tid":786647,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T05:39:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/14423/%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE-%E9%80%9A%E4%BF%84%E9%96%80-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-14423/%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%EF%BC%9A%E9%80%9A%E4%BF%84%E9%96%80%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E6%87%89%E3%80%8C%E8%BD%89%E5%90%91%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E3%80%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F14423%2F%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE-%25E9%2580%259A%25E4%25BF%2584%25E9%2596%2580-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B-14423%2F%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25EF%25BC%259A%25E9%2580%259A%25E4%25BF%2584%25E9%2596%2580%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5%25E6%2587%2589%25E3%2580%258C%25E8%25BD%2589%25E5%2590%2591%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E3%2580%258D&d=U9OnEOAJg4rLPpZvfU9Q6P6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=fe7eeb82\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/14423/%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE-%E9%80%9A%E4%BF%84%E9%96%80-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-14423/%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%EF%BC%9A%E9%80%9A%E4%BF%84%E9%96%80%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E6%87%89%E3%80%8C%E8%BD%89%E5%90%91%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E3%80%8D</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2018/08/%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E9%97%9C%E4%BF%82-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-donald%20trump%20jr-20180819123825_2285_large.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2018%2F08%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25BE%258E%25E9%2597%259C%25E4%25BF%2582-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B-donald%2520trump%2520jr-20180819123825_2285_large.png&h=35361f65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普表示，在有關俄羅斯干擾2016年美國總統大選的「通俄門」調查，調查人員應該把方向轉向中國。他周六在twitter說：「所有那些只盯着俄羅斯的傻瓜們應該開始朝另外一個方向看，中國。」（All of the fools that are so focused on looking only at Russia should start also looking in another direction, China.）特朗普之前曾說，中國黑客可能曾經入侵美國民主黨的電子郵件系統。<br />\n<br />\n《華盛頓郵報》報道，「經過視北韓為最大的國家安全威脅的18個月後，特朗普總統愈來愈把他的注意力放在中國方面，採取更具對抗性的做法。專家說，這是美國政策的一個具有風險的轉變」。美國政府的《美國之音》則說，「中美目前正陷入一場愈演愈烈的貿易戰，這兩個世界最大的經濟體之間的對抗，被認為達到幾十年來新的高點」。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普在同一則twitter並說：「但是，如果我們頭腦明智、立場堅定並且胸有成竹，最後我們會跟所有國家都將相安無事。」他一直指摘有關他的競選團隊與俄羅斯有勾結的「通俄門」調查，是不公平的「獵巫行動」。<br />\n<br />\n《華郵》引述分析家說，美國對中國的敵意升高，意味特朗普和他的顧問有一個看法，「視這個共產主義國家是一個邪惡強權，也是直接競爭的敵手。中國影響力擴大，美國必須通過極端的反制手段予以挫敗。這是在華盛頓外交政策分析家之間廣泛流傳的觀點」。<br />\n<br />\n《華郵》引述華盛頓國際及研究中心的中國事務分析家葛來儀（Bonnie Glaser）說，看不到現任美國政府會有很多議題將與中國合作，「我認為，特朗普政府有一個共同看法，即中國是一個競爭者。華府這裏的做法，是聚焦如何有一個更加有效對付中國的競爭策略」。"},{"pid":"3744c608006a93eafa0c9ad0d256ad0c54c9fff9","tid":786647,"uid":34666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T05:41:19.000Z","msg":"克林頓希拉莉兩公婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc8d9370578b0a5a46ff42ba8adad7ea455a9b91","tid":786647,"uid":26752,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"3744c608006a93eafa0c9ad0d256ad0c54c9fff9","tid":786647,"uid":34666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T05:41:19.000Z","msg":"克林頓希拉莉兩公婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T05:55:01.000Z","msg":"賣國賊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前仲話會賣台奶支<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba236872e4a6c28a4acad56be4efb7989b8e330e","tid":786647,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3744c608006a93eafa0c9ad0d256ad0c54c9fff9","tid":786647,"uid":34666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T05:41:19.000Z","msg":"克林頓希拉莉兩公婆<img src=\"/a